276
00:13:47,243 --> 00:13:50,955
If I had the chance
to ask her out with my Wish Letter…

277
00:13:52,039 --> 00:13:54,458
Well, I did think about inviting her.

278
00:13:54,542 --> 00:13:55,376
I see.

279
00:13:55,459 --> 00:13:58,212
- So I feel like this is…
- That's crazy.

280
00:13:58,295 --> 00:14:00,881
Everything is destined by fate.

281
00:14:00,965 --> 00:14:03,259
- I completely agree.
- Yeah.

282
00:14:03,342 --> 00:14:05,177
Things don't go as planned.

283
00:14:05,261 --> 00:14:06,846
That's true.

284
00:14:06,929 --> 00:14:10,933
- Especially because we have no devices.
- Yeah.

285
00:14:11,016 --> 00:14:12,810
We can't ask people out easily.

286
00:14:13,310 --> 00:14:15,312
- Not in a casual way.
- Right.

287
00:14:15,396 --> 00:14:20,359
