it's not easy to ask people out casually.

288
00:14:20,442 --> 00:14:24,572
It makes you think about
how you should write it

289
00:14:24,655 --> 00:14:26,365
and how to convey your thoughts.

290
00:14:26,448 --> 00:14:28,617
It's completely different from texting.

291
00:14:28,701 --> 00:14:30,536
"You wanna grab coffee?"

292
00:14:31,537 --> 00:14:33,163
That's how you'd text it.

293
00:14:33,247 --> 00:14:38,002
But writing "Would you like
to go have coffee with me?"

294
00:14:38,085 --> 00:14:40,129
carries a different weight.

295
00:14:41,046 --> 00:14:42,464
But to me,

296
00:14:42,548 --> 00:14:46,468
I think this is a really good thing.

297
00:14:46,552 --> 00:14:48,429
Even after I go back to Japan,

298
00:14:49,889 --> 00:14:53,058
I would want to value the words I use.

