that spoke to me in college.

386
00:18:53,132 --> 00:18:54,341
- Every girl.
- Right?

387
00:18:54,424 --> 00:18:57,177
- I went to an all-boys school.
- I see.

388
00:18:57,261 --> 00:18:59,054
I also went to an all-boys school.

389
00:18:59,138 --> 00:19:01,765
So, at my entrance ceremony in college,

390
00:19:01,849 --> 00:19:04,226
