to all kinds of emotions.

604
00:30:14,020 --> 00:30:16,189
- Because we don't have anything.
- Yeah.

605
00:30:16,272 --> 00:30:18,608
- That's all we think about.
- Yeah.

606
00:30:18,691 --> 00:30:20,235
Like writing letters

607
00:30:20,985 --> 00:30:22,654
and meeting people.

608
00:30:22,737 --> 00:30:24,572
We don't have our phones,

609
