610
00:30:28,493 --> 00:30:31,329
It makes me think a lot

611
00:30:31,996 --> 00:30:33,414
about those things too.

612
00:30:34,541 --> 00:30:36,042
- I'll go first.
- Okay.

613
00:30:55,144 --> 00:30:57,564
Isn't the view just amazing?

614
00:30:57,647 --> 00:31:00,191
- It's a breathtaking view.
- Yeah.

615
00:31:00,275 --> 00:31:02,193
Could this get any better?

616
00:31:02,277 --> 00:31:03,820
This feels so nice.

617
00:31:04,779 --> 00:31:06,906
We improved a lot.

618
00:31:07,615 --> 00:31:08,825
In one day.

619
00:31:11,870 --> 00:31:13,204
That went far.

620
00:31:16,165 --> 00:31:17,750
Not bad.

