00:32:02,754 --> 00:32:04,839
These two always talk about the next day.

636
00:32:04,923 --> 00:32:06,591
- True.
- It happens naturally.

637
00:32:06,674 --> 00:32:08,801
What are you doing tomorrow?

638
00:32:08,885 --> 00:32:10,929
Tomorrow? Nothing.

639
00:32:11,012 --> 00:32:11,846
No?

640
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:13,598
Do you wanna eat ramen for lunch?

641
00:32:14,098 --> 00:32:15,975
- Ramen for lunch?
- Yeah?

642
00:32:16,059 --> 00:32:19,479
We'll meet at around one o'clock.

643
00:32:19,562 --> 00:32:21,522
- Let's go eat ramen. Yeah!
- Ramen!

644
00:32:21,606 --> 00:32:22,440
Yay!

645
00:32:22,523 --> 00:32:25,777
Have you done laundry here?

646
00:32:25,860 --> 00:32:26,986
No.

647
00:32:27,070 --> 00:32:28,905
Do you wanna go to a laundromat?

648
00:32:29,405 --> 00:32:31,449
- I was going to ask you too.
- Really?

649
00:32:31,532 --> 00:32:33,743
But I wasn't sure

650
00:32:34,661 --> 00:32:36,913
about asking a girl out to a laundromat.

651
00:32:36,996 --> 00:32:38,331
- I don't mind.
- Really?

652
00:32:38,414 --> 00:32:40,833
Yeah. I'm okay with it.

653
00:32:41,501 --> 00:32:45,588
I'll do whatever
just to spend time with you.

