00:33:05,525 --> 00:33:09,404
I think having
their digital devices taken away

660
00:33:09,487 --> 00:33:11,322
is starting to have an effect.

661
00:33:12,281 --> 00:33:13,741
They're starting

662
00:33:13,825 --> 00:33:16,452
to pay attention to their intuition

663
00:33:16,536 --> 00:33:18,871
and reflecting on themselves.

664
00:33:18,955 --> 00:33:20,164
They say things clearly.

665
00:33:20,248 --> 00:33:23,710
If you have a smartphone,
