the parachuting was available.

685
00:34:17,263 --> 00:34:19,849
- But he said it at that timing.
- Exactly.

686
00:34:19,932 --> 00:34:22,185
- He specified Day Nine.
- Right.

687
00:34:22,268 --> 00:34:26,397
It's after Days Seven and Eight,
where he could receive Wish Letters.

688
00:34:26,898 --> 00:34:29,859
It seems like he did the math perfectly.

689
00:34:29,942 --> 00:34:32,862
- Yudai knows Tohko definitely likes him.
- Yes.

690
00:34:32,945 --> 00:34:37,533
So what Yudai needs to confirm
is not his feelings towards Tohko,

691
00:34:37,617 --> 00:34:40,036
but the others' feelings towards him,

692
00:34:40,119 --> 00:34:43,539
and his feelings towards the other girls.

693
00:34:43,623 --> 00:34:45,374
He'll see on Days Seven and Eight.

694
00:34:45,458 --> 00:34:49,045
Even if that goes awry,
he can face Tohko on Day Nine.

695
00:34:49,128 --> 00:34:51,172
How will he face her feelings?

696
00:34:51,255 --> 00:34:53,132
- That's what it all hinges on.
- Yeah.

697
00:34:53,216 --> 00:34:56,010
- Kensuke told Nanami she was pretty.
- That was adorable.

698
00:34:56,094 --> 00:34:59,263
Kensuke said it clearly,
and Nanami asked him out for ramen.

699
00:34:59,347 --> 00:35:01,390
<i>- And to the laundromat.</i>
<i>- Yes.</i>

700
00:35:01,474 --> 00:35:04,352
He'll do whatever
just to spend time with Nanami.

701
00:35:04,435 --> 00:35:05,561
Oh my gosh!

702
00:35:05,645 --> 00:35:08,815
